    <div id="all-loading-page" class="all-loading-page hide" ></div>
    <div class="container container-login" id='main-page-container'>
      <div class="row row-content ">
        <div class="col-xs-12 login-content">
          

<div class="div-logo">
  
  
    
      <img id="logo-page1" src="https://www.bdo.com.ph/sites/default/files/images/generic_login/securities_logo.png"/>
    
    
  
</div>
          

<div class="div-mess">
  <div class="col-xs-12 mess-list w-bg">
    
    &nbsp;
    
  </div>
  
  
    <div class="col-xs-12 mess-list"><p>Log in using your BDO Online Banking Username and Password</p><p> If you don't have a BDO Online Banking account,<a href="https://www.mybdo.com.ph/fo/ribtermsandconditions"> click here</a></p></div>
  
  
</div>
          



<div class="login-form" onKeyUp="return checkSubmit(event)" >
  <form id="loginForm" name="loginForm" action="/onlinelogin/validateLogin.do" method="POST">

    <input type="hidden" id="app_code" name="app_code" value="bsc_ipms" />
    <input type="hidden" id="refNo" name="refNo" value="" />
    
    <input type="hidden" id="backURL" name="backURL" value="https://www.bdo.com.ph/securities/home" />

    <div class="field-text field-user">

      <label for="j_username"  >User ID</label>
      <input type='text' autocomplete='off' id='j_username' name='j_username' class="input-username" maxlength="30" />

    </div>
    <div class="field-text field-password">

      <label for="j_password"  >Password</label>
      <input type='password' autocomplete='off' id='j_password' name='j_password' class="input-password" maxlength="20" />

    </div>
    
    <div id="error" class="error-mess error" ><span onclick="focusToField('username','')" > Invalid User ID or Password. </span> <br /></div><script src="/onlinelogin/resources/js/util/util.js"></script>
    
    <div class="field-submit">
      <div class="col-xs-6 "><input id="btnCancel" type="button" value="Cancel" class="input-login"></div>
      
      
      
        <div class="col-xs-6 "><input id="btnLogin" type="button" value="Login" class="input-login"></div>
      
    </div>
  </form>

  

</div>


  <div class="div-mess">
    <div class="col-xs-12 mess-list-footer"></div>
  </div>


<script>removeClass('j_username','error');removeClass('j_password','error');addClass('username','error');</script>
<script src="/onlinelogin/resources/js/login.js"></script>

    <div class="footer-text"></div>

<script>

      window.location.assign( encodeURI( "https://www.bdo.com.ph/securities/home" ) );
    }
  }
</script>
